'''David Eugene "Moose" Morissette''' (born December 24, 1971) is a [[Canadians|Canadian]] Jiretired professional [[ice hockey]] [[forward (ice hockey)|forward]] who played 11 games in the [[National Hockey League]] for the [[Montreal Canadiens]]. He is most remembered for his famous fight with [[Bob Probert]] in which he won by TKO.
Morissette was born in [[Baie-Comeau]], [[Quebec]].
