'''Vincent Muda''' (born 14 August 1988 in [[Amsterdam]]) is a Dutch rower.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/mu/vincent-muda-1.html|title=Vincent Muda Bio, Stats, and Results|website=Olympics at Sports-Reference.com|language=en|access-date=3 September 2017}}</ref> He competed in the [[Rowing at the 2012 Summer Olympics – Men's lightweight coxless four|lightweight coxless four]] at the [[2012 Summer Olympics]].  Muda started rowing at [[Weesp]] rowing club together with his twin brother [[Tycho Muda|Tycho]].

